A youth was stabbed to death by his friends after a drunken brawl in D’Costa Layout, late on Sunday night. The deceased was identified as Gowtham (21), a resident of Vasanthnagar.Gowtham had been to a party with his friend Ajith, and the latter’s two friends at an under-construction building in D’Costa Layout. Police sources said a quarrel broke out between Gowtham and Ajith’s friends over a petty issue. One of them stabbed Gowtham in the chest.Pulakeshinagar police arrested Ajith and one of his friends. But, the man who stabbed Gowtham is absconding, the police said.Assistant directordies in accidentAn assistant director in Kannada films was killed on the spot after his bike hit a tree on Jnanabharathi campus early on Monday. The deceased, Sandeep V. Gowda (38), was a resident of Rajarajeshwarinagar and was not wearing a helmet at the time of the accident. He suffered severe head injuries and was brought dead to hospital.